         <string>Download (if needed) and load dipy's Sherbrooke 3-shell diffusion dataset as a vtkMRMLDiffusionWeightedVolumeNode named HARDI193. Cached at ~/.dipy/sherbrooke_3shell/ after the first download (~30 MB).</string>
        </property>
       </widget>
      </item>
     </layout>
